{"instruction": "관리자 게시판 목록 테이블 컴포넌트를 TypeScript로 작성해줘. rows를 BoardRow[]로 받고, 각 행에 수정/삭제 버튼을 두되 onClick 핸들러가 id: number를 받도록 타입을 붙여줘(BoardTable). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React from \"react\";\n\ninterface BoardRow {\n  postNo: number;\n  title: string;\n  writer: string;\n}\n\ninterface BoardTableProps {\n  rows: BoardRow[];\n  onEdit: (id: number) => void;\n  onDelete: (id: number) => void;\n}\n\nfunction BoardTable({ rows, onEdit, onDelete }: BoardTableProps) {\n  return (\n    <table className=\"board\">\n      <tbody>\n        {rows.map((row) => (\n          <tr key={row.postNo}>\n            <td>{row.postNo}</td>\n            <td>{row.title}</td>\n            <td>{row.writer}</td>\n            <td>\n              <button type=\"button\" onClick={() => onEdit(row.postNo)}>수정</button>\n              <button type=\"button\" onClick={() => onDelete(row.postNo)}>삭제</button>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        ))}\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default BoardTable;\n"}
{"instruction": "관리자 목록 페이지네이션 상태를 TypeScript로 작성해줘. page/totalPage를 가진 PagingState를 useState로 관리하고 페이지 변경 핸들러에 next: number 타입과 범위 가드를 붙여줘(AdminListPaging). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React, { useState } from \"react\";\n\ninterface PagingState {\n  page: number;\n  totalPage: number;\n}\n\nfunction AdminListPaging() {\n  const [paging, setPaging] = useState<PagingState>({ page: 1, totalPage: 1 });\n\n  const handlePageChange = (next: number): void => {\n    if (next < 1 || next > paging.totalPage) return;\n    setPaging((prev) => ({ ...prev, page: next }));\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"num_wrap\">\n      <button type=\"button\" onClick={() => handlePageChange(paging.page - 1)}>이전</button>\n      <span>{paging.page} / {paging.totalPage}</span>\n      <button type=\"button\" onClick={() => handlePageChange(paging.page + 1)}>다음</button>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default AdminListPaging;\n"}
{"instruction": "관리자 검색/필터 폼을 TypeScript로 작성해줘. searchCnd/searchWrd를 가진 SearchCondition 상태 객체와, select·input 공용 onChange를 React.ChangeEvent<HTMLSelectElement | HTMLInputElement>로 타입지정해줘(AdminSearchForm). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React, { useState } from \"react\";\n\ninterface SearchCondition {\n  searchCnd: string;\n  searchWrd: string;\n}\n\nfunction AdminSearchForm() {\n  const [condition, setCondition] = useState<SearchCondition>({\n    searchCnd: \"0\",\n    searchWrd: \"\",\n  });\n\n  const handleChange = (\n    e: React.ChangeEvent<HTMLSelectElement | HTMLInputElement>\n  ): void => {\n    const { name, value } = e.target;\n    setCondition((prev) => ({ ...prev, [name]: value }));\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <form className=\"search_wrap\">\n      <select name=\"searchCnd\" value={condition.searchCnd} onChange={handleChange}>\n        <option value=\"0\">제목</option>\n        <option value=\"1\">내용</option>\n      </select>\n      <input name=\"searchWrd\" value={condition.searchWrd} onChange={handleChange} />\n    </form>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default AdminSearchForm;\n"}
{"instruction": "관리자 수정 페이지에서 react-router의 useLocation().state를 안전하게 타입지정하는 예제를 TypeScript로 작성해줘. NoticeEditState 인터페이스를 정의하고 state를 'NoticeEditState | null'로 단언한 뒤 옵셔널 체이닝으로 읽어줘(NoticeEditPage). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React from \"react\";\nimport { useLocation } from \"react-router-dom\";\n\ninterface NoticeEditState {\n  nttId: number;\n  bbsId: string;\n}\n\nfunction NoticeEditPage() {\n  const location = useLocation();\n  const state = location.state as NoticeEditState | null;\n  const nttId: number = state?.nttId ?? 0;\n  const bbsId: string = state?.bbsId ?? \"\";\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"board_view\">\n      <h1>공지 수정</h1>\n      <p>글번호: {nttId}</p>\n      <p>게시판: {bbsId}</p>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default NoticeEditPage;\n"}
{"instruction": "관리자 수정 폼 제출 핸들러를 TypeScript로 작성해줘. React.FormEvent<HTMLFormElement>로 onSubmit을 타입지정하고, 제어 input들을 ManagerForm 상태로 묶고, 제출 시 필수값 가드를 넣어줘(ManagerEditForm). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React, { useState } from \"react\";\n\ninterface ManagerForm {\n  loginId: string;\n  managerNm: string;\n}\n\nfunction ManagerEditForm() {\n  const [form, setForm] = useState<ManagerForm>({ loginId: \"\", managerNm: \"\" });\n\n  const handleChange = (e: React.ChangeEvent<HTMLInputElement>): void => {\n    const { name, value } = e.target;\n    setForm((prev) => ({ ...prev, [name]: value }));\n  };\n\n  const handleSubmit = (e: React.FormEvent<HTMLFormElement>): void => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!form.loginId || !form.managerNm) {\n      alert(\"필수 항목을 입력하세요.\");\n      return;\n    }\n    console.log(\"submit\", form);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>\n      <input name=\"loginId\" value={form.loginId} onChange={handleChange} />\n      <input name=\"managerNm\" value={form.managerNm} onChange={handleChange} />\n      <button type=\"submit\">저장</button>\n    </form>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default ManagerEditForm;\n"}
{"instruction": "관리자 상세보기 컴포넌트를 TypeScript로 작성해줘. detail을 'NoticeDetail | null' props로 받아 null 가드(early return)로 TS18047을 피하고, 값이 있을 때만 필드를 렌더링해줘(NoticeDetailView). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React from \"react\";\n\ninterface NoticeDetail {\n  nttSj: string;\n  nttCn: string;\n  ntcrNm: string;\n}\n\ninterface NoticeDetailViewProps {\n  detail: NoticeDetail | null;\n}\n\nfunction NoticeDetailView({ detail }: NoticeDetailViewProps) {\n  if (!detail) {\n    return <p className=\"no_data\">조회된 데이터가 없습니다.</p>;\n  }\n  return (\n    <div className=\"board_view\">\n      <h2>{detail.nttSj}</h2>\n      <span className=\"writer\">{detail.ntcrNm}</span>\n      <p>{detail.nttCn}</p>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default NoticeDetailView;\n"}
{"instruction": "JSX 숫자/불리언 속성 타입을 올바르게 쓴 관리자 폼 필드 컴포넌트를 TypeScript로 작성해줘. colSpan={n}, tabIndex={0}, cols={30}/rows={10}, readOnly를 문자열이 아닌 올바른 타입으로 지정해줘(AdminFormFields). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React from \"react\";\n\ninterface AdminFormFieldsProps {\n  colSpan: number;\n  message: string;\n}\n\nfunction AdminFormFields({ colSpan, message }: AdminFormFieldsProps) {\n  return (\n    <table className=\"board\">\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td colSpan={colSpan} className=\"no_data\">{message}</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            <textarea cols={30} rows={10} readOnly defaultValue=\"\" />\n            <input type=\"text\" tabIndex={0} readOnly defaultValue=\"\" />\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default AdminFormFields;\n"}
{"instruction": "관리자 핸들러에서 console.group/groupEnd를 올바르게 쓴 예제를 TypeScript로 작성해줘. console.groupEnd()는 인자 없이 호출(TS2554 회피)하고 useCallback 핸들러에 반환타입 void를 붙여줘(AdminLogPanel). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React, { useCallback } from \"react\";\n\ninterface CatalogItem {\n  ctlgNo: number;\n  ctlgNm: string;\n}\n\nfunction AdminLogPanel() {\n  const retrieveList = useCallback((): void => {\n    console.group(\"AdminLogPanel.retrieveList()\");\n    const items: CatalogItem[] = [];\n    console.log(\"count : \", items.length);\n    console.groupEnd();\n  }, []);\n\n  return (\n    <button type=\"button\" onClick={retrieveList}>조회</button>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default AdminLogPanel;\n"}
{"instruction": "상태 배지를 렌더 콜백으로 그리는 관리자 테이블을 TypeScript로 작성해줘. rows: AdminRow[]와 renderBadge 콜백(status를 받아 React.ReactNode 반환)을 props 인터페이스로 타입지정해줘(StatusBadgeTable). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React from \"react\";\n\ninterface AdminRow {\n  id: number;\n  name: string;\n  status: \"Y\" | \"N\";\n}\n\ninterface StatusBadgeTableProps {\n  rows: AdminRow[];\n  renderBadge: (status: AdminRow[\"status\"]) => React.ReactNode;\n}\n\nfunction StatusBadgeTable({ rows, renderBadge }: StatusBadgeTableProps) {\n  return (\n    <table className=\"board\">\n      <tbody>\n        {rows.map((row) => (\n          <tr key={row.id}>\n            <td>{row.name}</td>\n            <td>{renderBadge(row.status)}</td>\n          </tr>\n        ))}\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default StatusBadgeTable;\n"}
{"instruction": "관리자 목록을 useState 배열 + useEffect fetch로 불러오는 컴포넌트를 TypeScript로 작성해줘. NoticeItem[] 상태와 NoticeResponse 응답 형태를 정의하고 fetch().then 체인에 타입을 붙여줘(AdminNoticeList). 코드만 출력.", "input": "", "output": "import React, { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\n\ninterface NoticeItem {\n  nttId: number;\n  nttSj: string;\n}\n\ninterface NoticeResponse {\n  result: {\n    resultList: NoticeItem[];\n  };\n}\n\nfunction AdminNoticeList() {\n  const [list, setList] = useState<NoticeItem[]>([]);\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    fetch(\"/admin/notice\")\n      .then((res: Response) => res.json())\n      .then((data: NoticeResponse) => {\n        setList(data.result.resultList ?? []);\n      });\n  }, []);\n\n  return (\n    <ul className=\"board\">\n      {list.map((item) => (\n        <li key={item.nttId}>{item.nttSj}</li>\n      ))}\n    </ul>\n  );\n}\n\nexport default AdminNoticeList;\n"}
